{"tid":1993525,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"DQ郭榮鏗公職 林鄭：用人唯才","createTime":"2020-04-28T23:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T00:41:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c729e0625a46b1749537ce57c8c3f14002a456b","tid":1993525,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T23:48:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200429/7TMGEXNK2NQ2C5YBEYVNTHZ4MI/?code=5ea8bfa043181e00114f1ded&amp;clientId=a383471b-58aa-4e30-b726-6fd6fa215141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200429%2F7TMGEXNK2NQ2C5YBEYVNTHZ4MI%2F%3Fcode%3D5ea8bfa043181e00114f1ded%26clientId%3Da383471b-58aa-4e30-b726-6fd6fa215141&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImIDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=5bdcf0e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200429%2F7TMGEXNK2NQ2C5YBEYVNTHZ4MI%2F%3Fcode%3D5ea8bfa043181e00114f1ded%26clientId%3Da383471b-58aa-4e30-b726-6fd6fa215141&h=ea6f3038\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200429/7TMGEXNK2NQ2C5YBEYVNTHZ4MI/?code=5ea8bfa043181e00114f1ded&amp;clientId=a383471b-58aa-4e30-b726-6fd6fa215141</a><br />\n<br />\nDQ郭榮鏗公職 林鄭：用人唯才<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200429/large/1588091436_6d2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200429%2Flarge%2F1588091436_6d2b.jpg&h=311e6344&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名民主派區議員發表「議會戰線立場聲明書」，當中包括鄺葆賢及岑敖暉。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近日不斷遭港澳辦、中聯辦批評拖延立法會內會選主席的法律界議員、公民黨郭榮鏗，日前突然不獲續任競爭事務委員會委員，外界質疑有政治報復之嫌，特首林鄭月娥昨於行會前見記者，稱外界所指六年任期限制非硬指標，強調任命標準是用人唯才。郭榮鏗回應指自己是否人才，相信市民自有判斷。<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗上任競委會委員只有兩年，但政府前日發出該會任命名單，與郭同期任命的八人都獲續任，只有他一人不獲續任，外界質疑有政治報復之嫌，以DQ公職懲罰郭拖延內會選主席。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郭：政府幾時先謙卑學習<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：內會選主席遭兩辦施壓 區議員促寸土必爭 公民黨：不退縮<br />\n<br />\n林鄭昨被問是否不會讓反對政府措施的議員擔任公職時稱，......."},{"pid":"b38e77f6cff79e9a7aac212aa876b958ab27c933","tid":1993525,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T00:08:24.000Z","msg":"奴才個才"},{"pid":"7a8e45d47e606e239d31d97729fc1ba90b33186b","tid":1993525,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T00:09:00.000Z","msg":"用人為<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">奴</span></span>才"},{"pid":"490e4b1eb85505b544da26b6b0bbb4ed379cad6a","tid":1993525,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T00:41:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">條777重未死咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}